{"tid":2510941,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"國安處拘捕一男一女　28 歲男被指涉嫌「煽動分裂國家」　據悉與上水母子出售胡椒球彈槍案有關","createTime":"2021-04-30T13:32:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T14:41:37.000Z","uid":52779,"like":18,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"b38d5c59daf43a81b819cc722ef0037f34132af6","tid":2510941,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:32:51.000Z","msg":"警方公佈，國家安全處今日（30 日）拘捕一名 28 歲男子及 22 歲女子，兩人正扣留調查，男被捕者涉嫌「煽動分裂國家」等罪行。據了解，案件與早前一對母子，涉嫌在網上出售胡椒球槍的案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n警方指，國家安全處經調查後，今日在長沙灣拘捕一名 28 歲男子，涉嫌「煽動分裂國家」、「無牌經營槍械」及「藏有攻擊性武器」；以及在將軍澳拘捕一名 22 歲女子，涉嫌「無牌經營槍械」。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，案件與去年九月，上水一對母子涉嫌在網上出售胡椒球彈槍一案有關，兩母子涉嫌「無牌管有槍械及彈藥」、「未經許可輸入戰略物品」及「藏有攻擊性武器」被捕。警方追查此案時，今日再拘捕上述一男一女。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/a-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%99%95%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-28-%E6%AD%B2%E5%8F%8A-22-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fa-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-28-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%258F%258A-22-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&d=SQXEpmicj55cx%2FeODTqnT%2BaWbb7ReRbDtXxzMsl%2FlTw%3D&h=86547c57\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fa-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E8%2599%2595%25E6%258B%2598%25E6%258D%2595-28-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%258F%258A-22-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3-%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25AD%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E7%2585%25BD%25E5%258B%2595%25E5%2588%2586%25E8%25A3%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25B6%2F&h=e1a13784\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/a-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E8%99%95%E6%8B%98%E6%8D%95-28-%E6%AD%B2%E5%8F%8A-22-%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3-%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E7%85%BD%E5%8B%95%E5%88%86%E8%A3%82%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6/</a>"},{"pid":"45112ca16e8127f8ef3c58924d8ff824c0cadaa6","tid":2510941,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2064fba9ea4a8678f0e8e1860f0856edf3bd6afc","tid":2510941,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eae3aaf25b2bd53bb7cb656a52f17936ca39beb","tid":2510941,"uid":289966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:34:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bfc391f4e3945451d3106fcdd36f2b19d36965","tid":2510941,"uid":59801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:34:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7046c0e7ecd85f797086151a6701b56dc09c6098","tid":2510941,"uid":239266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b042bfa790b08edcb5763d0a72b49a09ff42197","tid":2510941,"uid":52779,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTim